command:chatgpt

** SchemaCrawler ChatGPT integration

api-key
OpenAI API key

api-key:env
OpenAI API key, from an environmental variable value

model
ChatGPT model
Optional, defaults to 'chatgpt-3.5-turbo'

timeout
Number of seconds to timeout a request if no response is received
Optional, defaults to 10

context
Number of chat messages (not tokens) to maintain as chat context
Optional, defaults to 10

use-metadata
Allow sharing of database metadata with OpenAI to enhance chat responses
Optional, defaults to false

Add command options to the `execute` command in the SchemaCrawler Shell
